query:
SELECT p.id, c.name as country, s.name as service, s.smshubCode, p.apiId, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
WHERE p.apiId IS NULL
LIMIT 20;
